149
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,330
Není třeba.

150
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:45,820
Mami, mami.

151
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:48,350
Je to moje dcera.

152
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:52,400
Ona je moje; Solova dcera.

153
