199
00:15:55,010 --> 00:15:57,030
Ale celou tu dobu se to snažil vynahradit!

200
00:15:57,030 --> 00:16:01,100
Strýc Mi Shaofei a Ou Qiang, můj táta se je snažil dostat oba zpátky.

201
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:03,190
